{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2015-01-28-saekano/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"少年读书隙中窥月"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"535aedd5-97ee-56cf-babd-06962f13b86b","excerpt":"本季新番之中最喜欢两部作品，《幸腹涂鸦》和《不起眼女主角的培育方法》。前者是有新房和龙轮的加成，还有梅津泰臣神一样的 OP…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b7b616b9653db4cfd945b07138d8d6d0/eea4a/Ohys-Raws-Saenai-Heroine-no-Sodatekata-02-CX-1280x720-x264-AAC.mp4_snapshot_22.00_2015.01.23_23.35.57.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[Ohys-Raws] Saenai Heroine no Sodatekata - 02 (CX 1280x720 x264 AAC).mp4_snapshot_22.00_[2015.01.23_23.35.57]\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b7b616b9653db4cfd945b07138d8d6d0/1c72d/Ohys-Raws-Saenai-Heroine-no-Sodatekata-02-CX-1280x720-x264-AAC.mp4_snapshot_22.00_2015.01.23_23.35.57.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b7b616b9653db4cfd945b07138d8d6d0/a80bd/Ohys-Raws-Saenai-Heroine-no-Sodatekata-02-CX-1280x720-x264-AAC.mp4_snapshot_22.00_2015.01.23_23.35.57.jpg 148w,\n/static/b7b616b9653db4cfd945b07138d8d6d0/1c91a/Ohys-Raws-Saenai-Heroine-no-Sodatekata-02-CX-1280x720-x264-AAC.mp4_snapshot_22.00_2015.01.23_23.35.57.jpg 295w,\n/static/b7b616b9653db4cfd945b07138d8d6d0/1c72d/Ohys-Raws-Saenai-Heroine-no-Sodatekata-02-CX-1280x720-x264-AAC.mp4_snapshot_22.00_2015.01.23_23.35.57.jpg 590w,\n/static/b7b616b9653db4cfd945b07138d8d6d0/a8a14/Ohys-Raws-Saenai-Heroine-no-Sodatekata-02-CX-1280x720-x264-AAC.mp4_snapshot_22.00_2015.01.23_23.35.57.jpg 885w,\n/static/b7b616b9653db4cfd945b07138d8d6d0/fbd2c/Ohys-Raws-Saenai-Heroine-no-Sodatekata-02-CX-1280x720-x264-AAC.mp4_snapshot_22.00_2015.01.23_23.35.57.jpg 1180w,\n/static/b7b616b9653db4cfd945b07138d8d6d0/eea4a/Ohys-Raws-Saenai-Heroine-no-Sodatekata-02-CX-1280x720-x264-AAC.mp4_snapshot_22.00_2015.01.23_23.35.57.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>本季新番之中最喜欢两部作品，《幸腹涂鸦》和《不起眼女主角的培育方法》。前者是有新房和龙轮的加成，还有梅津泰臣神一样的 OP 设计。后者则是完全地被角色所萌到了，整整一周多整个人都莫名其妙地兴奋和忧愁，一集动画看了四五遍。这样的感觉是好久没有了。</p>\n<p>也许我对于卖萌的世界感到乏味了，所以见到刻意设定的普通人主角，反而有一种莫名其妙的新鲜感。再加上惠本身面无表情的吐槽和正常到脱线的棒读式应答，使得剧情中充满了各种笑点。当然，这部作品本身内容编排得当，剧情节奏很好，也真的很懂得如何营造捏他，实在是超出了我的预期。</p>\n<p>硬要从心理上解释的话，也可能是我意识到自己是普通人，潜意识中也希望出现这么一个普通的女主角了吧。看来最近不管是千寻也好，惠也好，从名字和设定上更接近现实的女性角色总能更贴近我的萌点。</p>\n<p>既然开写了，写一些在内容上比较顺便的事情吧。最近购买了一个 wildcard 的 SSL 证书，整个日志都转向了 https。看到有一个属于自己的小锁图标还是很开心的，只不过这样一来就得多鼓捣一些别的东西了，要不然这 VPS 和这证书就都白白浪费了。</p>\n<p>日志的主题也随手改了一下，顺利变成了单列，比之前的自感觉有进步，但还是不怎么达标，不过要继续改的话就可能要伤筋动骨了，只好徐图之。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"不起眼女主的狂热","publish_date":"2015-01-28T22:52:11.000+08:00","revise_date":"2015-01-28T22:52:11.000+08:00","draft":false}}},"pageContext":{"previous":{"id":"6e8b2213-5027-5490-b02f-22458b7e6a86","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2015-01-17-juzhen-fangsong/","type":"blog","timeToRead":{"words":258,"minutes":2}},"frontmatter":{"title":"聚珍仿宋","publish_date":"2015-01-17T03:05:17.000+08:00"}},"slug":"/blog/2015-01-28-saekano/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1330398833","2356112386"],"slicesMap":{}}